Affiliations




                About Us


                    While our core investing principles remain constant, we have a history of innovation,
                    interweaving our human capital with technology. The name “Teak Hill” evokes the
                    idea of both timeless strength and resilience.

                     
                

                    Credit Capital’s senior team is comprised of investment management and asset management
                    professionals, who excelled in previous leadership positions at respected institutions.
                    They are complemented by experienced managers, analysts and staff. Together they
                    form a close-knit team who are significant investors in our offerings alongside
                    our limited partners and shareholders.

                     

                    Credit Capital Investments is a registered investment adviser with the United States
                    Securities and Exchange Commission.

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     

                     







