Credit Capital LLC





















































 



 
 





 
 








  



 
 







 



 




























































































 



  
 



Investing in the Nation's Communities
We Create Value in Affordable Housing                        


                               Read More                            



 









Credit Capital is a real estate investment firm located in Westlake Village, California. Our primary focus is as an equity sponsor of affordable housing investments throughout the country. Equity financing includes Section 42 federal Low Income Housing Tax Credit (LIHTC), state LIHTC and state and federal Historic Tax Credit (HTC). We offer a specialized level of service to our clients based on over 35 years of direct experience in all facets of the affordable housing industry. We continually seek partnerships with developers that demonstrate a clear commitment to building a strong real estate portfolio that serves the housing needs of America’s families and seniors. 










 

























